Port Sesefron was a space station in the Pleiades system. It was near the planet Sesefras Magna, and was a docking place for Xaxisian battleships and other spacecraft visiting the star system. Ford Prefect once took an Escape-O-Buggy from the sales ship he left in orbit around Epun to Port Sesefron, which was a three-day journey. Zaphod Beeblebrox once bought spray-on pants from Port Sesefron.From chapter 3 of And Another Thing.... Novels 
